I spent about 20 hours on the phone.

179
00:14:37,343 --> 00:14:40,244
- And you stayed with it the full time?
- Yes, sir.

180
00:14:40,613 --> 00:14:43,480
- How did it end?
- He came out. He gave himself up.

181
00:14:43,616 --> 00:14:44,913
